bug.author: awsaf49
bug.summary: wandb: ERROR Error while calling W&B API: Error 1062: Duplicate entry '189160-gbp6y2en' for key 'PRIMARY' (<Response [409]>)
bug.description: Whenever I try to create a new run (--name) on the same --project in YOLOv3 I get this error, wandb: ERROR Error while calling W&B API: Error 1062: Duplicate entry '189160-gbp6y2en' for key 'PRIMARY' (<Response [409]>). Changing the --project name temporarily solves the problem but then a new project needs to be opened for each run. But YOLOv5 runs smoothly without any trouble. I even tried training v3 using the v5 repo but was getting the same error.
